1) Open your generated hexagonal nanowire in Ovito and export it as a lammps data file with the extension >>>ldata<<<. Provide a proper filename
Example: HexWire_AlMishin1999_x110_y111.ldata

2) Provide the nanowire data file name and the interatomic potential details in "TMS_Nanowire_relaxation.lmpin"

3) Run the energy minimization. NOTE: The stopping criterion must be "Force tolerance"


